org.prebake.js
Class Console

java.lang.Object
  org.prebake.js.Console

@ParametersAreNullableByDefault
public final class Console
extends java.lang.Object

A FireBug-like console interface for JavaScript.

This is public so that the JS executor can find methods reflectively. It is not meant to be used outside this package otherwise.
